I"Z<p>One of the many advantages of the MacOS, is the fact that you can burn a cd from the finder, no extra software needed. This works best with internal CDRW drives but will also work with <a href="http://www.apple.com/itunes/compatibility/">supported external CDRW drives</a>. I was using my Powerbook G4 with combo drive for this tutorial.</p>

